{"tid":155133,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"在不久將來,美麗的概念會唔會全球統一？","createTime":"2017-03-13T19:32:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T00:01:01.000Z","uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54fde7c8e53ed171bc90c431348ce353df0b3175","tid":155133,"uid":77643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T19:32:45.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲打覺得喺不久嘅將來入面，人類對於「美麗」嘅概念會唔會趨向統一<br />\n<br />\n當中嘅概念可以係指對一個人嘅外表，又或者係一幢大廈嘅建築設計風格，甚至係一個人嘅心靈思想<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以點解大家會鍾意J同一個女優為例，因為大家都鍾意大波長腿，就自然公認左佢係一個靚女<br />\n但係正所謂百貨應百客，一啲豬西都總會有人覺得佢正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁究竟其實人類對於「美麗」嘅概念或者會唔會因為全球化之類嘅原因而變得統一呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知各位巴絲又點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9b8014a738334d5e6efefbfb8cc2c14e1d6edb","tid":155133,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T20:14:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.alisongenevieve.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/09/IMG_4801.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.alisongenevieve.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F09%2FIMG_4801.jpg&h=8021602d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b120ac37d375ed8c027d7006233a341bb5871b4c","tid":155133,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T22:54:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ecf26dda4c843663fb40eb8ed9f489addfb97807","tid":155133,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T22:54:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"84572d2abb42da9b03766b7d7d4f13479e752ce7","tid":155133,"uid":31796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T23:24:01.000Z","msg":"遲啲美麗=黑妹/蝻亞妹<br />\n你唔讚成=歧視"},{"pid":"33da6ba37dd32dd1a74b3c2a6c972b88d2111a77","tid":155133,"uid":9034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T00:01:01.000Z","msg":"唔會<br />\n<br />\n鬼佬鍾意食嘅亞洲人，不了"}]}